      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-06-02T13:05:44Z",
      "messageBody": "Keep subagent model selection on the legacy harness state path so v0 behavior remains unchanged while HarnessCompat derives only session model and mode from v1 sessions.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
