      "committedDate": "2026-06-02T13:05:45Z",
      "messageBody": "This PR does not need changeset entries yet, so remove the changesets added for the harness v1 and HarnessCompat work.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
