      "committedDate": "2026-06-02T13:05:45Z",
      "messageBody": "Session now owns state machinery (getState, setState, updateState,\nschema validation, update queue). Harness only passes stateSchema and\ninitialState config to created sessions. HarnessCompat composes legacy\nharness state with session-owned state and session-derived fields\n(currentModelId, modeId).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (zai-coding-plan/glm-5.1) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
      "messageHeadline": "refactor(core): move state ownership from Harness v1 to Session",
      "oid": "5b9c9445c85a3e16973cec8a6edb7095896bfa14"
    },
    {
