        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-06-02T19:41:30Z",
      "messageBody": "Use the Harness request-context getter when reading composed state so v1 session-derived fields are included without assuming a direct state snapshot is present.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
