      "committedDate": "2026-06-03T09:17:17Z",
      "messageBody": "Add v1 harness tool composition, permission and subagent config plumbing, and canonical workspace Skill support for session skill APIs. This removes the separate HarnessSkill shape so configured skills use the same Skill/SkillMetadata model as workspace-discovered skills.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
      "messageHeadline": "feat(core): add v1 harness tools and canonical skills",
      "oid": "bdc92b48672811719314495c42b8a833cdb8987e"
    },
