          "name": "Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5)"
        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-06-03T09:21:30Z",
      "messageBody": "Do not forward legacy MastraCode subagent definitions into the new Harness v1 subagent registry yet. The legacy shape does not declare agentId and subagents are still executed by HarnessCompat/v0 until the v1 subagent runtime is implemented.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
